Package: segregR
Type: Package
Title: Spatial segregation metrics in R
Version: 0.1.0
Author: 
    person("Marcus", "Saraiva", email = "marcus.saraiva@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Maintainer: The package maintainer <yourself@somewhere.net>
Description: This package makes it easy to calculate segregation metrics  in R. 
    The metrics implemented are *generalised*, *spatial*, and *global* / *local* 
    versions of the Dissimilarity index, and Theil's Entropy and Information 
    Theory indices (metrics of evenness), and the Isolation and Exposure indices.
